		"notes": "\n\t<p><i>This enormous beast has a shaggy, elephant-like body with a cluster of fanged, ghoulish humanoid heads writhing from long necks. </i></p>\n\t<p></p>\n\t<p><strong>AC</strong> 11, <strong>HP</strong> 15, <strong>ATK</strong> 1 bite (near) +7 (1d8 + paralyze), <strong>MV</strong> near, <strong>S</strong> +5, <strong>D</strong> +1, <strong>C</strong> +2, <strong>I</strong> +0, <strong>W</strong> +1, <strong>Ch</strong> -3, <strong>AL</strong> <strong>C</strong>, <strong>LV</strong> 2</p><p></p>\n\t<p><strong>Create Spawn</strong>. Humanoids killed and not completely consumed by a ghoulspawn hydra rise as ghouls 2d6 rounds after death.</p><p></p><p><strong>Heads</strong>. Choose how many heads the beast has. Each is LV 2, AC 11, HP 15, and can make 1 bite attack. A killed head sprouts into 2 new heads at the start of the beast’s turn unless doused with holy water or targeted by a bless spell beforehand. The beast’s LV is all the heads combined.</p><p></p><p><strong>Paralyze</strong>. DC 14 CON or paralyzed 1d4 rounds.</p><p></p><p><strong>Undead</strong>. Immune to morale checks.</p><p></p>",
